tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_data(
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  health_condition VARCHAR,
  readmission_status VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    weight FLOAT,
    height FLOAT,
    bmi FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE HealthIndicators (
    health_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    blood_pressure VARCHAR(20),
    heart_rate INT,
    glucose_level FLOAT,
    cholesterol_level FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE health_indicators (
  indicator_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID REFERENCES patients(patient_id),
  bmi FLOAT,
  blood_pressure VARCHAR(20),
  cholesterol INT
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
  admission_date DATE,
  discharge_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE MedicalRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
  treatment VARCHAR(100),
  doctor_name VARCHAR(50),
  record_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE VitalSigns (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  heart_rate INT,
  blood_pressure VARCHAR(20),
  temperature DECIMAL(5,2),
  oxygen_level DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE ReadmissionRates (
  readmission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  readmission_date DATE,
  readmission_reason TEXT,
  readmission_rate DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    admission_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE medical_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    treatment VARCHAR(100),
    admission_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE vital_signs (
    sign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    heart_rate INT,
    blood_pressure VARCHAR(20),
    oxygen_level INT,
    temperature FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE readmission_history (
    readmission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    admission_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE,
    readmission_date DATE,
    reason VARCHAR(200)
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    insurance_status VARCHAR(50)
);
